\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But the reason for a contract is to protect both parties ideally from the other doing some wrong or not fulfilling their side of the agreement.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And while the American economy is built on CONTRACTS, God's economy is built on COVENANTS.\
